included.description: The purpose of the project was to come up with the technological solution to one of the many problems that people face in developing countries. In regards to MSU's continuous ICT4D study abroad program in Tanzania, the group found that the number of students who do not graduate from secondary schools is very high in Tanzania and that became an issue that the group tried to tackle in this project. It was decided to build a web-based tool that would allow teachers to send short text (SMS) messages to students with prep materials for the National Examination.
included.title: Sparty Prep
